<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,335,602]" pageId="1" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,302,455,481]" pageId="1" pageNumber="53">Habitat.</emphasis>
The Serra da Maravilha is a mountainous massif located in the municipality of Senhor do Bonfim. The vegetation of the Serra da Maravilha can be characterized as a semideciduous seasonal forest (SEMARH 
<number box="[290,354,536,562]" pageId="1" pageNumber="53" value="2007.0">2007</number>
).
</paragraph>
